{"type": "article", "id": 28293, "title": "Cath Kidston 与迪士尼合作，以及，推荐一个睡衣品牌｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-16T11:16:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 28369, "name": "裙装"}, {"id": 1395, "name": "婚纱"}, {"id": 228, "name": "以色列"}, {"id": 25682, "name": "睡衣"}, {"id": 25228, "name": "碎花"}, {"id": 14651, "name": "九月刊"}, {"id": 13495, "name": "封面"}, {"id": 9, "name": "意大利"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 1899, "name": "Cath Kidston"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 13753, "name": "Rag&Bone"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 29046, "name": "The Billionaire Boys Club"}, {"id": 14878, "name": "Reformation"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 129, "name": "Kate Moss"}, {"id": 726, "name": "Pharrell Williams"}, {"id": 441, "name": "NIGO"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703122630zZjqc0Tbd9JwDaeL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/15/11949932/rag-bone-david-neville-CEO\"><b>Rag&amp;Bone CEO 辞职</b></a>｜Rag&amp;Bone 联合创始人 David Neville 从首席执政官这一职位上辞职，他在董事会的职位将不会被取代，仍参与公司事务。曾担任公司联席首席执行官的  Marcus Wainwright 将成为公司唯一的 CEO，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/marcus-wainwright-becomes-sole-ceo-at-rag-bone-10457452/\">他表示 David 将不会离开 Rag&amp;Bone</a>，而是脱离 CEO 日常繁重的事务，有精力投身于更多商业尝试。他还在采访中告诉 BOF，下一步将帮助作为彩妆艺术家的妻子 Gucci Westman 建立自己的美妆及护肤品牌。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/6/nike-head-of-basketball-business-resigns\"><b>Nike 篮球部门高管离职</b></a>｜Nike 全球篮球品类部门总经理兼副总裁 Michael Jackson  离职，他在这一职位上度过了两年的时间，将由在公司有 27 年经验的Craig Zanon 取代，后者此前曾掌管 Nike 篮球部门七年，最近管理 Nike 全球训练分支。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Guess-presents-first-sustainable-denim-line,703944.html\"><b>Guess 推出首个生态友好牛仔产品线</b></a>｜成衣品牌 Guess 首次推出可持续发展的牛仔产品线，作为春夏一个特别的胶囊系列。从生产工艺到面料（有机棉）和装饰品原料的选择都致力于减少对环境的影响，并采用特殊的生产程序，来减少水及其它能源的消耗、温室气体的排放。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Cath-Kidston-to-launch-seasonal-collections-with-Disney,703321.html\"><b>Cath Kidston 将推出迪士尼合作系列</b></a>｜英国品牌 Cath Kidston 将与迪士尼推出合作系列，预计将持续几季，迪士尼的经典角色会成为 Cath Kidston 的印花，首个 Disney x Cath Kidston 系列将使用维尼熊和伙伴们的形象。预计于 9 月 26 日起在 Cath Kidston 线上及实体门店售卖。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/15/11943736/kendall-jenner-vogue-cover-september\"><b>Kendall Jenner 或将登 Vogue 九月刊封面</b></a>｜据美国周刊（ Us Weekly）透露，作为每年时尚大刊的重头戏 Vogue 九月刊，很可能由 Kendall Jenner 拍摄封面，Vogue 方面表示不予置评。<br></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这里有一个来自<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/nufferton-unisex-pyjamas\">斯德歌尔摩的新品牌  Nufferton</a>，专注于设计更好的睡衣，均价在 110 欧元一套：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122618SaoRDtevWEkjTsuJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122619KEJT0QI5kuNziUR8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122619OHCrtnIvymgG8zKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122620KvFDjhXybxYdaWB4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122620IKyT0L6kxWq8vBAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122621o5fuiPaWl9qkr4BL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122621DC8NkZJyncBAzFes.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">创立于 1995 年的以色列婚纱品牌<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/berta-bridal-fall-2016-dresses/\"> Berta 发布 2016 秋冬系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122622kALhJYIy321Fojrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122622dbqK73IHAyTCmwR1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122623JVoQGaCENW6yS92l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122623jOvgTxoR69KBGp0F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122624wWsoB61qQnYvzc2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031226242DzpjwBsNkfGXJRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122624PIlFrVf4DqKT1Ck6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122625cFMZ3betQE2xWNp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">推荐 8 款 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/cute-dresses-summer-2016-shop/\">Reformation 夏季的裙装</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122625SzkENlfjicBuYneO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122626cyBfhUdwDnMgOjiI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122626Qo7vyELsdTV3IiJR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/kate-moss-daughter-lila-grace-vogue-italia-cover/#ixzz4BhkPT5xX\">Kate Moss 与女儿 Lila Grace 为意大利版 Vogue 六月刊拍封面</a>:</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122627dhHGa8zPERfTQuwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47792208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>Pharrell Williams 与日本潮流教父 Nigo 合作创立的潮牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/billionare-boys-club-summer-2016-capsule-collection\">The Billionaire Boys Club（亿万少年俱乐部）发布 2016 夏季系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122627J10CnOLtu3YhRgQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122627hpEvm20H13SdDTUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122628e5Vq2aQms9JuU0Rd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122628vE64jMWm3ZoL7hRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122629sKXCr7RY93M2S0fA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312262907E4y9AWae3JS6GD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}